            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/03/30/my-latest-interview-with-financial-survival-network-creating-a-decentralized-world/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to My Latest Interview with Financial Survival Network – Creating a Decentralized World">My Latest Interview with Financial Survival Network – Creating a Decentralized World</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2014-03-30T20:11:14+00:00">Sunday Mar 30, 2014</time> at 8:11 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/03/30/my-latest-interview-with-financial-survival-network-creating-a-decentralized-world/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on My Latest Interview with Financial Survival Network – Creating a Decentralized World">Leave a comment</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>Creating an ever connected, yet increasingly decentralized world is no easy task. Nevertheless, it is something I believe humanity must do in order to traverse the current challenging times and come out the other side better off than before.</p>
<p>Yesterday, I highlighted what I believe is an extremely important article on the <strong><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/03/29/the-co-op-movement-a-decentralized-solution-to-solving-inequality-and-avoiding-serfdom/">worker co-op movement.</a></strong> Earlier in the week, I sat down with Kerry Lutz of Financial Survival Network to discuss everything from Bitcoin and crony capitalism, to marijuana legalization and local food.</p>
<p>You can listen to the interview <a href="http://hwcdn.libsyn.com/p/7/8/0/780fe1a1f96b1d62/Michael_Krieger_26.Mar.14.mp3?c_id=7010998&amp;expiration=1396233753&amp;hwt=7190906a32cb45c82d94da54a905a693">here</a>. Enjoy!</p>
<div style=display:inline-block;>
<div style=float:left;margin-right:6px;>
<a href=bitcoin:1LefuVV2eCnW9VKjJGJzgZWa9vHg7Rc3r1><img src=http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/lbk-post-donations.png></a>
</div>
<div style=margin-top:16px;margin-left:70px>
