                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/03/05/my-latest-interview-with-wall-street-for-main-street-technology-bitcoin-and-the-u-s-economy/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to My Latest Interview with &#8220;Wall Street for Main Street&#8221; – Technology, Bitcoin and the U.S. Economy">My Latest Interview with &#8220;Wall Street for Main Street&#8221; – Technology, Bitcoin and the U.S. Economy</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2014-03-05T17:54:55+00:00">Wednesday Mar 5, 2014</time> at 5:54 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2014/03/05/my-latest-interview-with-wall-street-for-main-street-technology-bitcoin-and-the-u-s-economy/#respond" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on My Latest Interview with &#8220;Wall Street for Main Street&#8221; – Technology, Bitcoin and the U.S. Economy">Leave a comment</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>Yesterday, I had the pleasure to record another podcast with Jason Burack of <a href="http://www.wallstformainst.com">Wall Street for Main Street.</a> This is the first interview I&#8217;ve done in a little while, and it went quite a bit longer than either of us expected. I always enjoy doing these podcasts, as it allows me to express myself in a different format and explore topics I don&#8217;t have a chance to get to in my writings.</p>
<p>I&#8217;ve already heard excellent feedback on this one, let me know what you think.</p>
<p>Enjoy!</p>
